This paper deals with logical reasoning about knowledge and awareness, which is a topic closely related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also presents a sound and complete axiomatization for a logic, which falls under the category of mathematical logic (cs.LO). The paper also discusses game theory (cs.GT) and decision making (cs.MA) in the context of reasoning about knowledge. Finally, the paper deals with formal languages and syntax (cs.CC) in the context of associating different languages with different worlds in the model.
